      "description": "You can use the systemlib definitions by assembling them together with\nthe following lines in your build script:\n\n```bash\nmkdir -p ./third_party/systemlibs\ncp -ap \"${PREFIX}/share/bazel/systemlibs/absl\" third_party/systemlibs/\n```\n\nYou will also need an override in the top-level `MODULE.bazel`:\n\n```python\nlocal_path_override(\n    module_name = \"abseil-cpp\",\n    path = \"./third_party/systemlibs/absl\",\n)\n```",
